# Portfolio Project Rules

## Project Overview
Complete portfolio rebuild using Next.js + Tailwind CSS + TypeScript for assem.me

## Tech Stack
- Next.js 13+ (App Router)
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- Framer Motion (animations)
- MDX (blog posts)
- shadcn/ui (components)

## Development Guidelines
- Use TypeScript for all components
- Follow Next.js App Router conventions
- Implement proper SEO optimization
- Ensure excellent Core Web Vitals
- Never hardcode credentials - use encrypted/env vars
- Execute commands one at a time for safety

## Hosting & Deployment
- Target: Vercel or Netlify
- Domain: Currently at Cloudflare
- Performance: Optimize for speed and accessibility